{"tid":1525103,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"各位爸媽 同學仔 你地識做啦","createTime":"2019-08-31T19:40:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-01T03:55:43.000Z","uid":31220,"like":11,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"105cf1ee4a96082a66f42e8ff2daae1b6bb4b66d","tid":1525103,"uid":31220,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T19:40:07.000Z","msg":"電視直播住成個恐怖襲擊<br />\n你唔係放心比個仔/女同個恐怖分子二代做朋友呀？<br />\n容乜易學左佢地咁暴力呀<br />\n<br />\n有恐怖分子二代同學既你地<br />\n記得唔好圍住人啦<br />\n人地會驚會用警報器<br />\n唔好搵水淋濕哂佢啲野呀<br />\n唔好踩污糟人地枱枱凳凳<br />\n人地會嬲左自己爸媽架嘛<br />\n仲要唔好講佢知 因為佢老豆母係恐怖分子 先搞佢呀<br />\n佢係唔會驚架<br />\n唔好搞爛人地啲書呀文具呀<br />\n唔好畫花人地塊面<br />\n矇眼都唔好 人地咪認唔到自己同學囉<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1caf1f76d2df8291a9a3d1ec57aee3a6b83f04a5","tid":1525103,"uid":31220,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T19:40:19.000Z","msg":"1/10"},{"pid":"09718db628c51c1bfa408854b01cca425ff25fa9","tid":1525103,"uid":31220,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T19:40:30.000Z","msg":"2/10"},{"pid":"d0bd45724f244e94bd30ff5822ba8cd82fd84351","tid":1525103,"uid":98926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T19:40:37.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">聽日去機場可以嘅<br />\n搭鐵去荃灣/東涌/青衣<br />\n轉的士</span></strong></span><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">一人一架車先易塞</span></strong><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">巴士有排都逼唔夠一架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YwSqHBd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYwSqHBd.jpg&h=46853d82&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"44ac309a088c3b8e499b1ec28308ce766718ebba","tid":1525103,"uid":31220,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T19:40:49.000Z","msg":"3/10"},{"pid":"a7de3861d